OL,4,Caction after 'gaslighting' over
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FIn December, Work and Pensions
OL,8,FSecretary Liz Kendall said taxpayers
OL,9,Fcould not afford what could be a #10.5
OL,10,Fbillion compensation package for the
OL,11,Fwomen.
OL,13,FOn Monday, the Waspi campaign sent a
OL,14,F"letter before action" to the
OL,15,FDepartment for Work and Pensions
OL,16,Fwarning of High Court proceedings if
OL,17,Fthe issue is not resolved.
