OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FWaspi Chairwoman Angela Madden said
OL,8,Fmembers will not allow the DWP's
OL,9,F"gaslighting" of Waspi women to go
OL,10,F"unchallenged".
OL,12,FWaspi campaigners says the
OL,13,FGovernment's reasons for rejecting the
OL,14,FParliamentary and Health Service
OL,15,FOmbudsman report, which found that the
OL,16,Fwomen should be paid up to #2,950
OL,17,Feach, are "legally wrong".
