OL,3,CWaspi campaigners threaten legal
OL,4,Caction after 'gaslighting' over
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FThe group, which has launched a
OL,8,F#75,000 Crowdjustice campaign to fund
OL,9,Flegal action, says the Government has
OL,10,F14 days to respond before the case is
OL,11,Ffiled.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister, Chancellor Rachel
OL,14,FReeves and Work and Pensions Secretary
OL,15,FLiz Kendall were among the senior
OL,16,Fministers who backed the Waspi
OL,17,Fcampaign when Labour was in opposition.
