OL,3,CWaspi campaigners threaten legal
OL,4,Caction after 'gaslighting' over
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FAbout 3.6 million women in the UK were
OL,8,Faffected by the change, first
OL,9,Fannounced in the 1990s, to bring their
OL,10,Fretirement age in line with men.
OL,12,FThis was later accelerated under the
OL,13,FConservative-Liberal Democrat
OL,14,Fcoalition government more than a
OL,15,Fdecade ago.
OL,17,FHowever, there was a 28-month delay in
OL,18,Fwriting to inform them of the changes,
OL,19,Fwhich the Government accepted and
OL,20,Fapologised for.
