OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FThe Government previously highlighted
OL,8,Fresearch indicating that, by 2006, 90%
OL,9,Fof 1950s-born women knew about state
OL,10,Fpension age changes.
OL,12,FWaspi campaigners have claimed women
OL,13,Fsuffered financial hardship and had to
OL,14,Frethink retirement plans.
OL,16,FMs Madden said: "The Government has
OL,17,Faccepted that 1950s-born women are
OL,18,Fvictims of maladministration, but it
OL,19,Fnow says none of us suffered any
OL,20,Finjustice.
