OL,3,CWaspi campaigners threaten legal
OL,4,Caction after 'gaslighting' over
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,F"We believe this is not only an
OL,8,Foutrage but legally wrong."
OL,10,FA Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,11,Faccept the Ombudsman's finding of
OL,12,Fmaladministration and have apologised
OL,13,Ffor there being a 28-month delay in
OL,14,Fwriting to 1950s-born women.
OL,16,F"However, evidence showed only one in
OL,17,Ffour people remember reading and
OL,18,Freceiving letters that they weren't
OL,19,Fexpecting and that by 2006 90% of
OL,20,F1950s-born women knew that the state
OL,21,Fpension age was changing.
